reviewText: I thoroughly enjoyed this travelogue with the lovely and funny Joanna Lumley.  Mongolia actually looks like a great place to visit.  Russia not so much.  Note that this DVD is Region 4.  If you live in the U.S. and don't know what that means, don't buy it.
Joanna Lumley is the queen of travel. Her documentaries are always very informative and extremely entertaining. She's got charm, wit, beauty, and brains... she's really got it all!
